      "review_summary": "The branch adds `openclaw skills uninstall <slug>` with dry-run, confirmation, JSON, global/agent options, plus lifecycle helpers that remove ClawHub skill directories and lockfile entries.\n\nPR surface: Source +195, Tests +4. Total +199 across 3 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the review findings. Source inspection of the PR head shows the owner-mismatch, lifecycle fallthrough, and strict bare-slug paths, while current-main tests document the owner-qualified and legacy tracked behavior they should preserve.",
